## § 2.0 Component Props

All icon components accept these props (via `$props()` rune):

| Prop | Type | Default | Purpose |
|------|------|---------|---------|
| `stroke` | string | `'currentColor'` | Icon stroke color |
| `fill` | string | `'none'` | Icon fill color |
| `size` | number | `24` | Width and height in pixels |
| `class` | string | `''` | Additional CSS classes |

## § 3.0 Import Pattern

```svelte
<script>
  import Abc from '$lib/icons/Abc.svelte'
</script>
```

## § 4.0 Color Integration

```svelte
<!-- Navigation bar icons -->
<Icon stroke="#76abae" />

<!-- Toolbar icons -->
<Icon stroke="#eeeeee" />

<!-- Active/highlight state -->
<Icon stroke="#76abae" />
```

## § 5.0 MUST NOT

- Hardcode SVG markup directly in components
- Use arbitrary colors outside the design system
- Forget size for icons in different contexts
- Omit aria-label on icon buttons
